Primedia released the inquiry’s report on 19 September 2019. On 9 July 2019, Primedia commissioned Advocate Terry Motau SC to conduct an independent inquiry into a complaint of editorial interference and censorship by Karima Brown, a former talk show host. Primedia released the inquiry’s report on 19 September 2019. Read the Report on Primedia’s inquiry into allegations of censorship and editorial interference by Ms Karima Brown below: Primedia Final Report 17092019 by Janice Healing on Scribd  This article first appeared on 702 : Outcome of inquiry into allegations of editorial interference at Radio 702